## Scope (Final & Locked)

Phase 10 introduces **deterministic execution replayability** without adding recovery, scheduling, or autonomy.

### Included Sub-Phases

| Sub-Phase | Name                                               | Status     |
| --------- | -------------------------------------------------- | ---------- |
| 10.1      | Deterministic Retry Engine                         | âœ… Complete |
| 10.2      | Execution Persistence for Replay                   | âœ… Complete |
